&lt;p&gt;expect - 自动交互脚本 &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cDovL3hzdGFyY2QuZ2l0aHViLmlvL3dpa2kvc2hlbGwvZXhwZWN0Lmh0bWw=&#34;&gt;http://xstarcd.github.io/wiki/shell/expect.html&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
